elements.name: Verify items in Mobile list page can be sorted by name.

steps.name: User opens the application "http://live.techpanda.org/index.php/" in the browser
Title of the page should be "Home page"
User clicks on the mobile menu
Tile of the page should be "Mobile"
User selects sort by drope down as name
all the products should be sorted by name.

elements.name: Verigy cost of product in list page and detail page are same.

steps.name: User opens the application "http://live.techpanda.org/index.php/" in the browser
User clicks on the mobile menu
In the list of all products read the cost of "SONY XPERIA" and note the cost
User clicks on SONY XPERIA mobile
user reads the cost of SONY XPERIA mobile in detail page
cost from list page and detail page should be same.

elements.name: Verify user can not add more products in the cart than available in the store.

steps.name: User opens the application "http://live.techpanda.org/index.php/" in the browser
User clicks on the mobile menu
User clicks on SONY XPERIA add to cart button
change QTY value to "1000" and clicks UPDATE button
user should get the error message.
User clicks on Empty Cart link in the footer of list of all mobiles
Cart should be Empty

elements.name: Verify user able to compare 2 products

steps.name: User opens the application "http://live.techpanda.org/index.php/" in the browser
User clicks on the mobile menu
user clicks on Add to compare link for 2 mobiles Sony Xperia and IPhone
click on compare button
pop up window should open and details of 2 products should be there.
close the po up window
